{"tid":237112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解仲未死]  梅媽再遭申請破產 庭上指控對方：好過做大耳窿","createTime":"2017-05-10T07:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T02:28:04.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4181d7ee16c614b2799a70ff110c65130f7e9588","tid":237112,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"一直為爭女兒梅艷芳遺產而屢次興訟的「梅媽」覃美金，因欠下訟費於2012年被頒破產令，命令於去年4月才獲解除。惟今年3月又因欠下2名破產案中的產業受託人10萬元訟費再遭呈請破產，高院今開庭處理。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反對呈請的梅媽在庭上聲言願意付款，但投訴呈請人短短個多月就將欠款增至13萬：「好過做大耳窿」，又指控對方將其中銀戶口凍結，令她未能還債，連生活費也無法提取：「佢都夠晒毒喇！吸血咁吸！」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n法庭著梅媽「唔好空口講白話」，決定押後案件下周至本月17日，讓梅媽向銀行取得凍結戶口確認信始再開庭。聆案官指，若兩呈請人一方面凍結覃的銀行戶口，另一方面又呈請她破產，「咁樣講唔過去」，下令要梅媽向銀行索取確認信，證明銀行已遭凍結，以及凍結申請人的資料及理由等。聆案官提醒，若申請凍結戶口的是另一些人，則梅媽未必可動用戶內的存款還債。"},{"pid":"3bba476a06f0f4bff56b76b16e35a8ab418e380e","tid":237112,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"貪字得個貪"},{"pid":"ae76a7e6d26fdd940a5e76ba45e0ea4331d119fb","tid":237112,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貪字得個貧</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bb9f8213f346ce8e4db2e728dd80b61a12e0f01a","tid":237112,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貪字得個貧</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b334fd056ffedee50072b981f4774022cb2f6e84","tid":237112,"uid":22574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貪字得個貪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ddb032b88a5b79b0981ae6004e7523dbac6db5","tid":237112,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"可能份遺產唔係一炮過比晒佢，先令到呢個老而不有啖氣到長命到而家，有d生存意志"},{"pid":"ff8745c616c561db1e12cbd7119f7892d90f262c","tid":237112,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能份遺產唔係一炮過比晒佢，先令到呢個老而不有啖氣到長命到而家，有d生存意志</blockquote><br />\n當初如果一炮俾晒佢, 咪幾年洗晒再申請綜援囉"},{"pid":"8171c1b64b0dc3b957ba6bc962d5857ec9877bf6","tid":237112,"uid":107539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"終極廢老系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8c0a41ae4eb78a98f017b3a5573ade1c8450d","tid":237112,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行過路過入黎睇下啦喂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼指大後又一垃圾學店</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n（各位DSE雞唔該入一入黎）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"517fe809cd95f94740b8c0618ebd66b7dfe3eb88","tid":237112,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afde84de7fd19532d543af8ecebdc8a4284e0f45","tid":237112,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b899990e074d95db74b11efc85a67a65cf1c97d","tid":237112,"uid":55256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢有乜嘢錯<br />\n點解要針對佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你訓左幾多年？"},{"pid":"0838ba92fafadf7ac3076e29ed09594fdd8eaff9","tid":237112,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係有必要咁對一個老人家?</blockquote><br />\n你都戇撚鳩<img src=\"